          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi guys\nI was a student in this money market.Let me explain in brief.\n1. Director is money minded. My whole batch was charged 7k for nothing. And 3of my frnds got charged 15k and the blame was that they have broken the TV . They asked for money when our parents went to the school for result and TC . They made their mess staff as the eye witness (about breaking the tv ) in front of our parents and as we were not present at that time they were able to trick our parents. I mean common of they are the eye witness then why do u ask money at that time.\n2. All the good ratings are from their staff , frnds and some got paid for giving good reviews obviously from the fines they have collected from us.\n3.About facilities\nNo working ac\nWorst food and some times we got insects in rice and curry.\nBroken and unhingenic bathrooms\n\nConsider this and never let ur child join this hell",
          "publisher": {
